data.description: TONS OF POTENTIAL *****4 bedroom 2 bathroom Pool Home with Carport. This home features Wood and Tile Floors throughout. Separate Living and Dining Room Areas, Kitchen includes Gas Stove, nice size Master bedroom, Second Bedroom does have a Sliding glass Door Glass door that enters to a small Private Covered Patio. Both Dining Room and Living Room Have Sliding Glass Doors that lead to your Covered Patiooverlooking the Pool and Nice Sized Fenced yard. Separate Laundry Room with Storage Area. This particular property is on City Water, City Sewer and also includes Gas for your Hot Water Heater and Stove. Pool Equipment is Newer and Gas Hot Water Heater is Approximately 1 year old. This property has tons of potential!! Does Need TLC, could be great as an Investment as well a Primary. Non HOA
